result.title: Wish there could be more early contests...
result.content:
19:30 PM in Moscow is 23:30 in China, so it is hard for people who feel sleepy early (like me) to take part in the contest...

I've noticed that at times there will be contests on 11:30 AM Moscow time , which is a favorable time for me and perhaps more students in China. Hope there could be more early contests so that I can increase(drop) my rating :)
